'''A·W·F·爱德华兹'''（{{lang-en|Anthony William Fairbank Edwards}}，笔名'''A. W. F. Edwards'''）是一位英国统计学家、[[演化生物学|演化生物学]]家和[[遗传学家|遗传学家]]，是外科医生[[哈罗德·C·爱德华兹|哈罗德·C·爱德华兹]]之子，医学遗传学家[[約翰·赫頓·愛德華茲|約翰·赫頓·愛德華茲]]之弟，曾师从[[羅納德·愛爾默·費雪|羅納德·愛爾默·費雪]]，主要科普作品有《心灵的嵌齿轮：维恩图的故事》（''Cogwheels of the Mind: The Story of Venn Diagrams''）等<ref>{{cite book |author-first=Rasmus Grønfeldt |author-last=Winther |date=2018 |title=Phylogenetic Inference, Selection Theory, and History of Science: Selected Papers of A. W. F. Edwards with Commentaries |publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] |isbn=9781107111721 |location=Cambridge, U.K. |page=519 |url=https://www.cambridge.org/de/academic/subjects/life-sciences/genetics/phylogenetic-inference-selection-theory-and-history-science-selected-papers-w-f-edwards-commentaries |access-date=2020-09-15 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815031238/https://www.cambridge.org/de/academic/subjects/life-sciences/genetics/phylogenetic-inference-selection-theory-and-history-science-selected-papers-w-f-edwards-commentaries |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

